body:
Pretty sure this is the end to this series based on how the author chose to introduce the new girls.
Basically, it's a throwback to how everything started in chapter 1, and it seems like the coach was somewhat forced to leave the previous school (likely to do with the lady investigating him). This allows the MC to cut his ties with all the girls cleanly (?), so his senpai can now no longer cheat (lmao) and no idea what the other chicks are gonna do.

Seems a bit of a let down for such a long-running series, but I guess the author just wanted to put it to an end, the releases were no longer as consistent in the past, so likely the author just didn't have the zeal to keep it running anymore. Probably just wanted it to end. I would like to be wrong tho, some girls were quality.

This series now joins the ranks of Succubi Supporter and Fela Pure in the hentai Hall of Fame.
